sources.title: Ghosters Phantom Patrol | Full Movie | Action Adventure
sources.description:
Ghosters Phantom Patrol - When ghostly phantoms escape from an underground government facility, chaos, terror and whimsy abound. Who will the fate of humanity and those who are not so rested in peace depend upon to save the day? Fate rests in two unlikely security guards, teaming up to save New York City from the paranormal infestation?
2023.  Stars: Gio Drasconi, Arthur Gazarian, Cuan Snyman
